---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Ken Chang"
	description="Ken Chang's profile, education, work experience, technical interests, and language skills."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-05-11')}
>
	<p>
		Hello, I am Ken Chang. I graduated from Fu Jen Catholic University with a BBA in
		Information Management, and later received an M.S. in Computer Science and Information
		Engineering from National Taipei University of Technology.
	</p>

	<p>
		My interests sit around cloud, software engineering, computer graphics, machine learning,
		crypto, and computer hardware. I have worked with PHP, Java, Python, HTML, CSS,
		JavaScript, React, Laravel, Spring Boot, PyTorch, OpenGL, and Three.js.
	</p>

	<h2>Education</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>
			<strong>National Taipei University of Technology</strong>, M.S. in Computer Science and
			Information Engineering, Computer Graphics Laboratory, 2021-2023.
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Fu Jen Catholic University</strong>, BBA in Information Management, 2017-2021.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Experience</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>
			<strong>E.SUN Bank</strong>, Software Engineer Intern, 2021. I worked on a computer auction
			website and an electronic payment system.
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>National Taipei University of Technology</strong>, Teaching Assistant for Discrete
			Mathematics and Computer Animation assignments.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Languages</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Chinese: native</li>
		<li>English: B1-B2, TOEIC 745</li>
		<li>French: beginner</li>
		<li>Japanese: beginner</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		This site started on WordPress and is now migrated to Astro. The older posts are kept
		selectively: mostly articles that still have technical or personal value, rather than a full
		archive of every old announcement or outdated service review. You can find the main archive
		on the <a href="/blog/">blog page</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
